{"tid":1818343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【地鋪大劈價】業主趕新年前出貨！","createTime":"2020-01-09T23:24:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-12T02:25:05.000Z","uid":202464,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"25de4fb40f91d1085b63610854a81e3195993fe9","tid":1818343,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T23:24:21.000Z","msg":"1.  旺角山東街47至51號星際城市地下1號舖，面積約830呎：<br />\n<br />\n目前租客「數碼通」，月租約45萬元。<br />\n<br />\n業主2018年放售叫價3.5億元，，回報率1.5厘，<br />\n現大劈價40%，至2.1億元，回報率增至2厘。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 花園街43號地下<br />\n<br />\n鞋店月租39萬元，<br />\n業主叫價由2億元減至1.3億元，減幅35%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3. 亞皆老街6號地下連閣樓，<br />\n<br />\n舖位現空置，業主叫價由1億元減至7,000萬元，仍乏人問津。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n4. 上環長達大廈地下A1至A5舖，面積約2,000方呎，<br />\n<br />\n租客「許氏找換店」月租達79萬元。<br />\n<br />\n業主原叫價2.6億元，回報率3.6厘，<br />\n<br />\n劈價27%，開1.9億，租務回報率將增至5厘。"},{"pid":"48804bdcd709025ecc5530d5f658e9956ffa720b","tid":1818343,"uid":62167,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T00:12:46.000Z","msg":"過億既世界<br />\n同我完全兩個時空"},{"pid":"8c3eb6e9380cec765bd1610180578ed97c3db727","tid":1818343,"uid":213877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T00:18:05.000Z","msg":"有平咩？"},{"pid":"c559b82df500c1d4d23b029a5a3d7ca16ce9d7d7","tid":1818343,"uid":34295,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T00:22:00.000Z","msg":"回報率點會追到啊<br />\n租金一樣跌啦"},{"pid":"e522b1c1400a97503b66fc5c4ad1e350ff1b9b32","tid":1818343,"uid":14422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T00:24:29.000Z","msg":"3. 亞皆老街6號地下連閣樓<br />\n<br />\n個閣樓係唔係僭建㗎？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0140663494be188a0675e088c554e2cc597f61cc","tid":1818343,"uid":65042,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-10T00:27:13.000Z","msg":"找換店都月租79萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a59a0046813e5c31aa37db26c3d1b44bb9ca4d1f","tid":1818343